{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"59168-small-bird-s-big-adventure","title":"Njem nnukwu Obere Nnụnụ","description":"Obere Nnụnụ hụrụ Onye Ukwu ahụ n'anya. Ma, olee ebe Onye Giant nọ? Obere Nnụnụ na-aga njem ịchọta ya","language":"Igbo","langCode":"ig","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nkem Osuigwe"],"illustrators":["Wesley van Eeden"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/59168-small-bird-s-big-adventure"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118247/size3/993a850d571731acbf727c386c72efb2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118247/size6/993a850d571731acbf727c386c72efb2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54631/size6/5ab5e6c9592d6b4d114a156944463631.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ dị nnọọ ntakịrị.\nỌ dị obere ma dị nnọọ ka nnụnụ.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54632/size6/c40898c1525127e7b4ce0da86c56b8e6.jpg","text":"3/23","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54633/size6/04f99e41b44360156edfa8ed5429e615.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ bi n'otu ụlọ mara mma ya na nnukwu Onye Ukwu.\nObere Nnụnụ hụrụ Onye Ukwu ahụ n'anya.\nỌ bụ ezigbo Onye.\nỌ nyere ya ọtụtụ obere ihe egwuregwu ụmụaka.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54634/size6/ac86b718311de7ecf9697b437d0ab1da.jpg","text":"5/23","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54635/size6/65a97e91d859e190959214773dd7aff9.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ dị mwute mgbe nnukwu Onye Ukwu ahụ anoghị.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54636/size6/0e208cb94a7986ea9b9f41b40cef25ee.jpg","text":"Ya mere, otu ụbọchị obere nnụnụ gara gaa chọta nnukwu Onye Ukwu.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54637/size6/89519e30e2c7f99d68bbc01004a2a8e0.jpg","text":"8/23","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54638/size6/4ffa908fb1e20e3201e3fb568e35c6ef.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ na-efe elu ruo mgbe o nwere ike\nlee ụwa dum.\nỌ chọrọ ịchọta Onye Ukwu ahụ.\nEbee ka ọ ga- ada ala?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54639/size6/44c85c635dfdd9c02cef1b796ffa443b.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ rutere n'oké ọhịa, jupụta na\nosisi na okooko osisi na akụ.\nObere Nnụnụ na-egwuri egwu na ya!\nMa, olee ebe Onye Ukwu ahụ nọ?","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54640/size6/b3bd14dd3ac577ac3489b285ba8f443b.jpg","text":"11/23","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54641/size6/4949a2d6bace00bc726b45508cf14387.jpg","text":"12/23","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54642/size6/d97a3ff9a80383e91a8647f555c6e345.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ na-aga na'ebe mbara igwe nke snow na'ada - nkume oyi si n'eluigwe\nỌ dị ọcha ma dị nro.\nObere Nnụnụ hụrụ nkume oyi si n'eluigwe n'anya na-agagharị na ya.\nMa, olee ebe Onye Ukwu ahụ nọ?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54643/size6/55ef7192dc0602c4f3a0c7bc631c9d19.jpg","text":"Oge a, obere nnụnụ na-ama elu karịa elu.\nỌ na-efe n'etiti kpakpando na ụyọkọ kpakpando! Ọ hụrụ ọnwa! Ọ hụrụ igwe egwu!\nMa, olee ebe Onye Ukwu ahụ nọ?","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54644/size6/9ef56a4c76802d90bc6dc70763331ffa.jpg","text":"15/23","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54645/size6/a92d12aa933fe3f9206b8076c6fc1fe5.jpg","text":"Site n'ụzọ dị elu, ya na anya ya dị egwu,\nObere Nnụnụ hụrụ ihe!\nGịnị ka ọ ga-abụ?","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54646/size6/6a22c12a0bf5a24045092b35541db178.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ na-agbada, ala, ala.\nEbee ka ọ ga-ada ala?","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54647/size6/13644a125b05cdc96e491a8e8b1621ce.jpg","text":"18/23","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54648/size6/53622666462c706373fd9ca3cb43c1e6.jpg","text":"19/23","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54649/size6/6e868ea5ea058bcd0c5c25946ad31b42.jpg","text":"Obere Nnụnụ ahụ nwetara onye ya n'aka Onye Ukwu ahụ!\nObi dị ya ezigbo ụtọ ịhụ ya.\n\"M hụrụ gị n'anya, Onye Ukwu!\" Ka ọ kwuru.","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54650/size6/a7e1c0c1f0aa89f37ce06665f62c9419.jpg","text":"Onye ukwu ahụ wetara obere nnụnụ nso ya.\n\"M hụkwara gị n'anya,\" ka Onye Ukwu kwuru.","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54651/size6/cccfc22e1c9ecf3444c6e314a45fccb5.jpg","text":"22/23","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54652/size6/26d6f1291bccaa5f117123b685cf8c99.jpg","text":"23/23","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":22,"words":263}}